==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Tantalic
<hw>Tan*tal"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>Of or pertaining to tantalum; derived from, or containing,
tantalum; specifically, designating any one of a series of acids
analogous to nitric acid and the polyacid compounds of
phosphorus.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tantalism</ent>⟦br⟧
